Database: IMDB
Tables: Movie, Artist, Roles, Review

i) Movie - Movie table have details Moviename, Artist, Directorname, Genre, Releasedate, Media  
ii) Review - Review table have details Moviename , Review 
iii)Artist - Artist table have details of Artistname , Skills
iv)Roles - Roles table have details of Artistname ,Moviename ,Roles 

create database IMDB;  # Database creation

Movie Table creation:

create table Movie(
Moviename varchar (50) Primary Key,
Artistname varchar(50),
Directorname varchar(50),
Genre varchar(50),
Releasedate date,
Media varchar(25));

